## Execute Installable Operations with PHP

```php
<?php

use Studio1902PeakCommandsModels\Installable;

// Create an installable instance from config
$config = [
    'name' => 'Call to Action',
    'handle' => 'call_to_action',
    'base_path' => base_path('vendor/studio1902/statamic-peak-commands/resources/blocks/call_to_action'),
    'operations' => [
        [
            'type' => 'copy',
            'input' => '_call_to_action.antlers.html',
            'output' => 'resources/views/page_builder/_call_to_action.antlers.html',
        ],
        [
            'type' => 'copy',
            'input' => 'call_to_action.yaml',
            'output' => 'resources/fieldsets/call_to_action.yaml',
        ],
        [
            'type' => 'update_page_builder',
            'block' => [
                'name' => 'Call to Action',
                'instructions' => 'Show a call to action.',
                'icon' => 'alert-alarm-bell',
                'handle' => 'call_to_action',
            ],
        ],
    ],
];

$installable = app(Installable::class, ['config' => $config]);

// Execute all operations in sequence
$result = $installable->install();

// The install method:
// 1. Resolves each operation type through the registry
// 2. Hydrates operation with installable context
// 3. Executes operation run() method
// 4. Returns updated installable for chaining

// Handles directory structures in handles:
// 'utilities/card' becomes handle='card' with filepath='utilities/'

```

## Fetch and Display Related Events (Twig)

```twig
{{ collection:{{ handle }} sort="{{ singular_handle }}_date_start:asc" {{ singular_handle }}_date_end:is_after="{ today }" :id:isnt="id" limit="3" as="items" }}
  {{ unless no_results }}
    {{ partial:typography/h1 as="h2" content="{ trans:strings.{{ handle }}_more }" class="md:col-span-12" }}
    {{ items }}
      {{ partial:components/{{ handle }}_item class="md:col-span-4" }}
    {{ /items }}
  {{ /unless }}
{{ /collection:{{ handle }} }}
```

## Render Main Desktop Navigation (Statamic)

```statamic
{{ nav:main max_depth="3" select="title|url|description|action_link" }}
{{ unless no_results }}
*   [{{ title }} {{ if children }}

    {{ svg:chevron_down attr:class="w-2 ml-1 overflow-visible stroke-current" attr:aria-hidden="true" }}

    {{ /if }}](#)
    {{ if children }}
    {{ children }}

    {{ title }}
    -----------

    {{ _total = children | count }}

    {{ children }}

    [

    ### {{ title }}

    {{ description }}

    ]({{ url }})

    {{ /children }}

    {{ if next }}

    {{ /if }}

    {{ /children }}
{{ /unless }}
{{ /nav:main }}
```

